## ─── Text Formatting ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

snippet bf "bold" i
\textbf{${1:${VISUAL}}}${0}
endsnippet

snippet it "italic" i
\textit{${1:${VISUAL}}}${0}
endsnippet

snippet ul "underline" i
